吳曉婷\r\n本件正本證明與原本無異\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　3 　　月　　4 　　日\r\n                              書  記  官  洪聖祐","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c422%2c20220315%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,422,20220315,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"422","JDATE":"20220315","JTITLE":"竊盜"}